Class AbstractFluid

net.multifusionlib.MultiFusionLib.fluid.AbstractFluid
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.minecraftforge.common.extensions.IForgeFluid, IFluid
public class AbstractFluid extends net.minecraftforge.fluids.ForgeFlowingFluid implements IFluid
AbstractFluid is a custom fluid class that extends ForgeFlowingFluid and implements IFluid interface. This class includes various properties and behaviors for the fluid such as temperature, color, viscosity, density, freezing capability, poisonous nature, and more.
